data.description: Your Dream Country Home Awaits! Escape to serenity in this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled on approximately 2.3 acres of picturesque country living. Embrace the tranquility of nature from your own screened porch or unwind on the quaint wood deck that overlooks the wooded backyard. With a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, this home offers optimal privacy and comfort for you and your loved ones. Enjoy the convenience of a separate laundry room, a welcoming foyer entrance, and ample storage space throughout. Outside, a spacious storage building provides room for all your outdoor essentials, while a long driveway ensures plenty of parking for guests. Revel in the peace and seclusion of your surroundings, where the beauty of nature awaits at every turn. Don't miss your chance to make this idyllic retreat your own. Schedule your private viewing and start living your country dream!
